  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 29eba545bae127f488175478b5cdcb00, type: 3}
  m_Name: JungleDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NpcDialogue
  npcName: JungleNPC
  dialogueLines:
  - Well, well... a traveler. You won't be needing those gems where you're going.
  - Be careful going deeper into the jungle.
  - The paths twist around, and it is easy to lose your way.
  - If you want to make it through, keep an eye out for gems hidden along the maze.
  - And watch for wolves. One of them has been roaming nearby.
  - If you spot something that looks a bit like me from far away, do not take chances.
